# Claude — UI design only

Apply **only** when designing, styling, or refactoring visual UI for this Jekyll site.

## Do not apply when

- Editing `_config.yml`, content data, analytics, or build scripts
- Non-visual questions

## Source of truth

`design/design-system.md` — **Organic / Natural** style (wabi-sabi, earth palette).

## Project knowledge (Claude Projects)

Upload:

1. `design/design-system.md`
2. `design/claude-project-knowledge.md`

## Stack

SCSS (`_sass/`), HTML includes (`_includes/`, `_layouts/`). Map tokens to SCSS; match partials and skins.

## Essentials

- Palette: rice paper `#FDFCF8`, loam `#2C2C24`, moss `#5D7052`, clay `#C18C5D`, sand `#E6DCCD`, timber `#DED8CF`
- Fraunces + Nunito/Quicksand; soft moss/clay shadows (not black, not hard offset)
- Grain texture overlay; organic blob radii; pill buttons/inputs
- Gentle motion: scale/lift hover, `active:scale-95` on buttons
- Blob washes, asymmetric cards, section background alternation
- Mobile-first; 48px touch targets; moss focus ring
